  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK827">
<l>colvaṇakka moṉṉārkaṭ koḷḷaṟka vilvaṇakkan </l>
<l>tīṅku kuṟittamai yāṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Since the bending of the bow bespeaks evil, one should not accept (as good) the humiliating speeches of one's foes.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
